//! ImpersonationRequest flow implementation
//!
//! Generated by backbone-schema
//!
//! Admin impersonation session request workflow:
//! - Validate request (admin cannot impersonate self)
//! - Check concurrent session limits
//! - Create impersonation session
//! - Monitor for expiration
//! - Log all actions during session

